# Phase 3: Validation and Testing (Q1 2026)

## Objective
Validate compliance with PCI-DSS v4.0 through audits and testing.

## Tasks
- Perform internal audits using updated Self-Assessment Questionnaires (SAQs).
- Engage a Qualified Security Assessor (QSA) for validation.
- Conduct network vulnerability scans to identify and remediate gaps.
- Obtain an Attestation of Compliance (AoC).

## Timeline
- Start: January 2026
- End: March 2026

## Deliverables
- Internal audit report
- Vulnerability scan reports
- Attestation of Compliance (AoC)
